<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Airbnb</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google Fonts - Poppins for headings, Inter for body text -->
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@600;700;800&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome for Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        h1,
        h2,
        h3 {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen flex flex-col antialiased">
    <%- include('../nav') %>

    <header class="bg-white shadow-md py-6 border-b border-gray-200">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
                About <span class="text-red-500">Airbnb</span>
            </h1>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">

        <!-- About Airbnb Section -->
        <section class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 pb-4 border-b-2 border-red-100 flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-building text-red-400 mr-3"></i>Our Story & Mission
            </h2>
            <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-lg">
                <p>
                    Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has
                    since grown to 4 million hosts who have welcomed more than 1.5 billion guest arrivals across
                    virtually every country in the world. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make
                    it possible for guests to belong anywhere.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our mission is to create a world where anyone can belong anywhere. We believe that by opening our
                    homes and sharing our lives, we can build a more connected and understanding world. We empower
                    millions of entrepreneurs and small businesses through our platform, fostering local economies and
                    sustainable tourism.
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                        <i class="fas fa-globe-americas text-blue-500 text-3xl mb-3"></i>
                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Global Community</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Connect with people worldwide.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                        <i class="fas fa-handshake text-green-500 text-3xl mb-3"></i>
                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Trust & Safety</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Your peace of mind is our priority.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-yellow-500 text-3xl mb-3"></i>
                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Unique Experiences</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Beyond just a place to stay.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Support System & Customer Care Section -->
        <section class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 pb-4 border-b-2 border-red-100 flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-headset text-red-400 mr-3"></i>24/7 Support & Customer Care
            </h2>
            <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-lg">
                <p>
                    Your comfort and security are paramount. Our dedicated global support team is available around the
                    clock to assist you with any questions, concerns, or emergencies you might encounter during your
                    Airbnb journey.
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200">
                        <i class="fas fa-phone-alt text-red-500 text-2xl mr-4"></i>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Phone Support</p>
                            <a href="tel:+1-800-123-4567" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">+1-800-123-4567</a> (Toll-Free, Global)
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope text-red-500 text-2xl mr-4"></i>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Email Support</p>
                            <a href="mailto:support@airbnb.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@airbnb.com</a> (Response within 24 hours)
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200">
                        <i class="fas fa-life-ring text-red-500 text-2xl mr-4"></i>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Help Center & FAQs</p>
                            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Visit our comprehensive Help Center</a> (Self-service articles)
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200">
                        <i class="fab fa-twitter text-red-500 text-2xl mr-4"></i>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Social Media Support</p>
                            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">@AirbnbHelp on Twitter</a> (Quick responses)
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
                    For immediate assistance, please call our phone support. For less urgent inquiries, email and our
                    Help Center are excellent resources.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Other Features / Why Choose Airbnb Section -->
        <section class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 pb-4 border-b-2 border-red-100 flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-star text-red-400 mr-3"></i>Why Choose Airbnb?
            </h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-lg">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200 border border-gray-200">
                    <i class="fas fa-home text-purple-500 text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Millions of Unique Stays</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">From treehouses to castles, find a place that truly inspires you.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200 border border-gray-200">
                    <i class="fas fa-hiking text-orange-500 text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Experiences by Locals</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Discover hidden gems and activities led by passionate locals.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200 border border-gray-200">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-green-500 text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Secure Payment System</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Book with confidence through our secure and encrypted platform.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200 border border-gray-200">
                    <i class="fas fa-users text-blue-500 text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Vibrant Community</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Join a global network of travelers and hosts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200 border border-gray-200">
                    <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt text-red-500 text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Explore the World</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Access millions of listings in over 220 countries and regions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200 border border-gray-200">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-indigo-500 text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Grow as a Host</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Earn income and share your space with travelers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Call to Action Section -->
        <section class="bg-red-500 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl text-white text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Experience Airbnb?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl">
                Whether you're looking for your next adventure or want to share your space with the world, Airbnb is
                your platform.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-6">
                <a href="/explore"
                    class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 border border-white text-lg font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm text-red-500 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-white transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105">
                    <i class="fas fa-search mr-3"></i> Find a Stay
                </a>
                <a href="/home/add-home"
                    class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 border border-white text-lg font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm text-white bg-transparent hover:bg-white hover:text-red-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-white transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105">
                    <i class="fas fa-plus-circle mr-3"></i> Become a Host
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

</body>

</html>